{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"mask","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/mask","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG 属性参考主页</a></p>\n\n<p><code>mask</code>属性绑定的元素将应用给定的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/mask\"><code>&lt;mask&gt;</code></a>元素。</p>\n\n<p>作为一个外观属性，它可以直接用作 CSS 样式表内部的属性。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法","title":"用法","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">类别</th>\n   <td>外观属性</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">值</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Content_type#funciri\" title=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en/SVG/Content_type#FuncIRI\">&lt;FuncIRI&gt;</a> | <strong>none</strong> | inherit</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">可变性</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">规范文档</th>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/masking.html#MaskProperty\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition)</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"funciri\"><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Content_type#funciri\" title=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en/SVG/Content_type#FuncIRI\">&lt;funcIRI&gt;</a></dt>\n <dd>对同一 SVG 文档片段内部别的图形对象的一个引用 ，这个图形对象将用作遮罩。这个引用的句法与<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/url\"><code>css uri</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>的句法相同。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下列元素可以使用<code>mask</code>属性：</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#container\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#Container\">容器元素</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#graphical\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#Graphical\">图形元素</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关内容","title":"相关内容","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/mask\"><code>&lt;mask&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"用法","id":"用法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"元素","id":"元素"},{"text":"相关内容","id":"相关内容"}],"summary":"« SVG 属性参考主页","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"mask","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"mask","locale":"fr","native":"Français"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/mask","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/mask/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG 属性参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/mask","title":"mask"}],"pageTitle":"mask - SVG | MDN","noIndexing":false}}